title: Sunlite 01670-SU G16.5 Globe Light Bulb 40 Watts, Candelabra Base (E12), 120 Volt, Clear, Incandescent, Dimmable, 1 Pack, 2600K Warm White
features: CANDELABRA BASE - With their candelabra base (E12) these Clear G16.5 Globe bulbs are suitable for use in many applications. Chandeliers, wall sconces, decorative lamps, pendant fixtures, sign displays, and more.
WARM WHITE LIGHT - These 40 watt traditional incandescent bulbs put out a comfortable warm white light at 2600K.
DIMMABLE - Adjust the light to suit your mood. When attached to a dimmer switch the 350 lumen output of these lamps can be adjusted from 100% to 1% and anywhere in between with no flickering.
CONVENIENT 1-PACK - Save money with this handy 1-pack.
MERCURY FREE - These bulbs contain no mercury or other harmful chemicals making them safe for the environment. Bulb measures 2.79 inches high, 1.96 inches in diameter.

description: These G16. 5 globe bulbs will compliment any fixture.
